 or be confused with the rare original structure, and instead, it should be true to its time. This philosophy manifests in the contemporary glass structure that frames downtown views and creates an intimate connection with the surrounding landscape.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/michael-hsu-reimagines-1800s-austin-home-for-contemporary-living/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-43/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-572471\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-43-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Exterior view of a modern building with large glass windows, revealing a lit-up interior with dining and living areas. Evening setting with reflections of trees in the glass.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-43-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-43-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-43-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-43.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/michael-hsu-reimagines-1800s-austin-home-for-contemporary-living/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-34/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-572469\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-34-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with abstract wall art, a black coffee table, two beige armchairs with brown cushions, a sculptural chair, and 