ffice-architecture-32-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern, spiral staircase with a wooden handrail curves around a tall, abstract black sculpture in a minimalist, well-lit space with light streaming through a window above.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-32-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-32-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-32-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-32.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/michael-hsu-reimagines-1800s-austin-home-for-contemporary-living/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-39/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-572470\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-39-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern interior with a curved staircase, large windows, and a view of a city skyline against a sunset. The walls are light-colored with a sconce, and there\u0026#39;s a table with decorative items.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-39-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-39-800x1066.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-39-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/03/travis-heights-historic-home-michael-hsu-office-architecture-39-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/i